data.description: Discover the epitome of comfortable and stylish living in this remarkable 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home nestled within the sought-after enclave of Blackberry Crossing. This property harmoniously combines thoughtful design, spacious interiors, and modern amenities to create an inviting haven for you and your loved ones.    Upon entering, you're greeted by an inviting eat-in kitchen, perfect for creating culinary delights and enjoying casual meals. The heart of the home unfolds into a generously sized family room adorned with a cozy fireplace, providing the ideal setting for relaxation and gatherings.    Adding to the allure of the main level is a versatile den, offering the flexibility to create a home office, playroom, or study space to suit your needs.    Retreat to the upper level, where the master suite awaits. With a full bath and a convenient walk-in closet, this private oasis offers comfort and convenience. Three additional well-appointed bedrooms provide ample space for family, guests, or personal hobbies.    Outdoor enjoyment is at your fingertips with a thoughtfully designed deck, providing the perfect spot for al fresco dining, entertaining, or simply savoring the tranquility of your surroundings. Completing this exceptional offering is a 2-car garage, ensuring both convenience and ample storage. Situated in the desirable Blackberry Crossing neighborhood, this home provides not only a sanctuary of modern living but also proximity to local amenities, parks, and schools. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite property your own. Schedule a showing today and experience the lifestyle that awaits in this remarkable home.
